e\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 559}, {\"ngram\": \"a military contingent\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"the nearby Avenue Foch\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Due to Olympic security measures, the number of troops were reduced compared to previous years.\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic security measures\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"troops\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"previous years\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some 4,000 people, down from 6,500 last year, and 162 horses marched in the tightly choreographed show.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some 4,000 people\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"162 horses\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"the tightly choreographed show\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No tanks or armored vehicles took part, but overhead more than 60 aircraft flew in formation, including a British Typhoon fighter alongside French Mirages and Rafales.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 964, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9992733804638462, \"rank\": 0.0006749782319525232, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 998, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.505261373725146, \"rank\": 0.7963014140834302, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No tanks\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"armored vehicles\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"fr